title: Best of The Program | Guest: Catherine Engelbrecht | 10/5/20
description:
The New York Times has finally found Antifa, or at least “insurrection anarchists.” Catherine Engelbrecht, founder & president of True the Vote, discusses how Biden’s Texas political director was implicated in a mail-in ballot scheme. Make sure to register to vote! Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer threatens to use “alternative sources of authority” to enforce her emergency COVID-19 declarations. The Pope has come out criticizing free market economics and advocating for wealth redistribution.
